# Smart Air Purifier with Dual Activated Carbon Filters

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
Air pollution inside households is a growing concern, especially in urban environments. Commercial air purifiers are often expensive and require frequent manual filter replacement.  
This project presents a **low-cost smart air purifier** that uses **activated carbon filters** and an **air quality sensor** to automatically maintain effective air purification.

The system intelligently switches between a **main filter** and a **sub (backup) filter** when the primary filter becomes saturated, ensuring continuous air purification with minimal user intervention.

